 202:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/hand.c ****         //
 203:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/hand.c ****         // Search DevicePath for a Hard Drive Media Device Path node.
 204:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/hand.c ****         // If one is found, then see if it matches the signature that was
 205:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/hand.c ****         // passed in.  If it does match, and the next node is the End of the
 206:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/hand.c ****         // device path, and the previous node is not a Hard Drive Media Device
 207:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/hand.c ****         // Path, then we have found a match.
